 .../dts/renesas/r8a774a3-hihope-rzg2m-ex-idk-1110wr.dts   | 15 +++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 16 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a774a3-hihope-rzg2m-ex-idk-1110wr.dts

